<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>LogsGo</title><link>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/</link><description>Recent content on LogsGo</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><atom:link href="https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Architecture</title><link>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/docs/architecture/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/docs/architecture/</guid><description>&lt;p>LogsGo is designed as a &lt;strong>single binary&lt;/strong> service with three main surfaces:&lt;/p>
&lt;table>
 &lt;thead>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;th>Surface&lt;/th>
 &lt;th>Default&lt;/th>
 &lt;th>Role&lt;/th>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/thead>
 &lt;tbody>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>gRPC&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>:50051&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Log ingestion (&lt;code>UploadLog&lt;/code>, &lt;code>UploadLogs&lt;/code>)&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>REST HTTP&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>:8080&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Query API, label discovery, metrics, pprof&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>Web UI&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>:19091&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Embedded dashboard for express queries and charts&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table>
&lt;h2 id="high-level-flow">High-level flow&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/images/archv1.png" alt="Architecture overview">&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Docker</title><link>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/deployment/docker/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/deployment/docker/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="build">Build&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">docker build -t logsgo:local .
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Root &lt;code>Dockerfile&lt;/code> and &lt;code>.dockerignore&lt;/code> define the image context.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="run">Run&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">docker run --rm -p 8080:8080 -p 50051:50051 -p 19091:19091 &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> -v logsgo-data:/data &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> logsgo:local &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --data-dir&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>/data
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Mount config files for store, TLS, and queue as needed:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Getting started</title><link>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/guides/getting-started/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/guides/getting-started/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="prerequisites">Prerequisites&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Go&lt;/strong> (see &lt;code>go.mod&lt;/code> for the module version)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Node.js / npm&lt;/strong> (only if you rebuild the UI)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Docker&lt;/strong> (recommended for the full example stack)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Optional: &lt;code>protoc&lt;/code> if regenerating gRPC stubs (&lt;code>make proto&lt;/code>)&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="option-a--interactive-docker-example-fastest">Option A — Interactive Docker example (fastest)&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git clone https://github.com/Saumya40-codes/LogsGO.git
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">cd&lt;/span> LogsGO/examples
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">docker compose up
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Then open:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>REST API</title><link>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/api/rest/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/api/rest/</guid><description>&lt;p>Base URL defaults to &lt;code>http://localhost:8080&lt;/code>. Authenticated deployments require &lt;code>Authorization: Bearer &amp;lt;jwt&amp;gt;&lt;/code> when &lt;code>--public-key-path&lt;/code> is set.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="get-apiv1query">&lt;code>GET /api/v1/query&lt;/code>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Run a LogsGoQL expression.&lt;/p>
&lt;table>
 &lt;thead>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;th>Query param&lt;/th>
 &lt;th>Required&lt;/th>
 &lt;th>Description&lt;/th>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/thead>
 &lt;tbody>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>expression&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>yes&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>LogsGoQL string&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>start&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>for range&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Start timestamp (API accepts formats parsed by the server)&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>end&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>for range&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>End timestamp&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>resolution&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>for range&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Step duration with &lt;code>s&lt;/code>/&lt;code>m&lt;/code>/&lt;code>h&lt;/code>/&lt;code>d&lt;/code> suffix&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table>
&lt;p>Invalid &lt;code>resolution&lt;/code> returns &lt;strong>400&lt;/strong> with an error payload.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Data model</title><link>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/docs/data-model/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/docs/data-model/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="log-entry">Log entry&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>A log is a structured record aligned with the gRPC &lt;code>LogEntry&lt;/code> message:&lt;/p>
&lt;table>
 &lt;thead>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;th>Field&lt;/th>
 &lt;th>Type&lt;/th>
 &lt;th>Description&lt;/th>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/thead>
 &lt;tbody>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>service&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>string&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Service or source identifier (queryable)&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>level&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>string&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Severity / level (e.g. &lt;code>info&lt;/code>, &lt;code>warn&lt;/code>, &lt;code>error&lt;/code>)&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>message&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>string&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Log body (supports &lt;code>CONTAINS&lt;/code> in LogsGoQL)&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>timestamp&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>int64&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Unix timestamp (client may omit; server can set “now”)&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>labels&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>map[string]string&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Custom key/value labels for richer filtering&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-protobuf" data-lang="protobuf">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">message&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nc">LogEntry&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">string&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kd">service&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">string&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">level&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">string&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kd">message&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">int64&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">timestamp&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">map&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kt">string&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">string&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">labels&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="series-and-aggregation">Series and aggregation&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Query results are often returned as &lt;strong>series&lt;/strong>: an entry shape plus a &lt;strong>count&lt;/strong> of matching occurrences in a window. Instant queries aggregate within the lookback; range queries produce points along the timeline.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Docker example</title><link>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/guides/docker-example/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/guides/docker-example/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="standard-example-examples">Standard example (&lt;code>examples/&lt;/code>)&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">cd&lt;/span> examples
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">docker compose up
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Typical services:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>logsgo&lt;/strong> — ingestion + API + UI&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>minio&lt;/strong> — S3-compatible bucket backend&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>example_app&lt;/strong> — sample producer (varies by compose file)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Config bind-mounts such as &lt;code>store_config.yaml&lt;/code>, &lt;code>queue-config.yaml&lt;/code>, &lt;code>prometheus.yml&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>Inspect &lt;code>examples/docker-compose.yml&lt;/code> and &lt;code>examples/store_config.yaml&lt;/code> for exact wiring.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>gRPC API</title><link>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/api/grpc/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/api/grpc/</guid><description>&lt;p>Package: &lt;code>logapi&lt;/code>&lt;br>
Proto: &lt;code>api/grpc/proto/logs.proto&lt;/code>&lt;br>
Generated Go: &lt;code>api/grpc/pb/&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="service">Service&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-protobuf" data-lang="protobuf">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">service&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">LogIngestor&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">rpc&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">UploadLog&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">LogEntry&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">returns&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">UploadResponse&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">);&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">rpc&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">UploadLogs&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">LogBatch&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">returns&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">UploadResponse&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">);&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="messages">Messages&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>LogEntry&lt;/strong> — &lt;code>service&lt;/code>, &lt;code>level&lt;/code>, &lt;code>message&lt;/code>, &lt;code>timestamp&lt;/code>, &lt;code>labels&lt;/code> map.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>LogBatch&lt;/strong> — &lt;code>repeated LogEntry entries&lt;/code>.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>UploadResponse&lt;/strong> — &lt;code>bool success&lt;/code>.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Helm / Kubernetes</title><link>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/deployment/helm/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/deployment/helm/</guid><description>&lt;p>Chart path: &lt;a href="https://github.com/Saumya40-codes/LogsGO/tree/main/charts/logsgo">&lt;code>charts/logsgo&lt;/code>&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;table>
 &lt;thead>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;th>Field&lt;/th>
 &lt;th>Value&lt;/th>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/thead>
 &lt;tbody>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>Chart name&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>logsgo&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>Chart version&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>0.1.0&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>App version&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>0.0.1&lt;/code> (chart metadata; override image tag)&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table>
&lt;h2 id="install">Install&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">helm install logsgo ./charts/logsgo -n logs --create-namespace
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="notable-values">Notable values&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Image&lt;/strong>: &lt;code>saumyashah40/logsgo&lt;/code>, tag &lt;code>dev&lt;/code> by default — set &lt;code>image.tag&lt;/code> for releases.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Service ports&lt;/strong>: HTTP &lt;code>8080&lt;/code>, gRPC &lt;code>50051&lt;/code>, web &lt;code>19091&lt;/code>.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Ingress&lt;/strong>: enabled by default (&lt;code>nginx&lt;/code> class), host example &lt;code>dashboard.myapp.local&lt;/code> → web UI port.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Security context&lt;/strong>: non-root (&lt;code>runAsUser: 1000&lt;/code>), drop all capabilities, no privilege escalation.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Service account&lt;/strong>: created by default.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Probes / HPA / secrets&lt;/strong>: templates included under &lt;code>charts/logsgo/templates/&lt;/code>.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="customize">Customize&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">helm install logsgo ./charts/logsgo &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --set image.tag&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>latest &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --set ingress.hosts&lt;span class="o">[&lt;/span>0&lt;span class="o">]&lt;/span>.host&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>logs.example.com &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --set &lt;span class="nv">replicaCount&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">2&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Mount store, TLS, and JWT material via Secrets and extra volumes (extend &lt;code>values.yaml&lt;/code> / deployment template as needed for your cluster).&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>CLI flags</title><link>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/api/cli/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://saumya40-codes.github.io/LogsGO/api/cli/</guid><description>&lt;p>Binary entrypoint: &lt;code>cmd/logsGo&lt;/code> (Cobra). Run &lt;code>./logsGo --help&lt;/code> for the build you have.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="storage--retention">Storage &amp;amp; retention&lt;/h2>
&lt;table>
 &lt;thead>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;th>Flag&lt;/th>
 &lt;th>Default&lt;/th>
 &lt;th>Description&lt;/th>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/thead>
 &lt;tbody>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>--data-dir&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>data&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Directory for local log data&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>--max-retention-time&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>10d&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Max time block chunks remain on disk (&lt;code>d&lt;/code>/&lt;code>h&lt;/code>/&lt;code>m&lt;/code>/&lt;code>s&lt;/code>)&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>--max-time-in-mem&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>1h&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Time logs remain in memory before flush&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>--max-logs-in-mem&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>10000&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Max in-memory logs before flush&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>--unlock-data-dir&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>false&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Allow other processes on data dir (not recommended)&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>--flush-on-exit&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>false&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Flush to next store on any exit for stronger persistence&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>--store-config-path&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;em>empty&lt;/em>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Path to S3-compatible store YAML&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>--store-config&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;em>empty&lt;/em>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Inline store config (exclusive with path)&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table>
&lt;h2 id="listen-addresses">Listen addresses&lt;/h2>
&lt;table>
 &lt;thead>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;th>Flag&lt;/th>
 &lt;th>Default&lt;/th>
 &lt;th>Description&lt;/th>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/thead>
 &lt;tbody>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>--http-listen-addr&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>:8080&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>REST API&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>--grpc-listen-addr&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>:50051&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>gRPC ingestion&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>--web-listen-addr&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>:19091&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Embedded web UI&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table>
&lt;h2 id="query">Query&lt;/h2>
&lt;table>
 &lt;thead>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;th>Flag&lt;/th>
 &lt;th>Default&lt;/th>
 &lt;th>Description&lt;/th>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/thead>
 &lt;tbody>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>--lookback-period&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>15m&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Instant query lookback from “now”&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table>
&lt;h2 id="security">Security&lt;/h2>
&lt;table>
 &lt;thead>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;th>Flag&lt;/th>
 &lt;th>Default&lt;/th>
 &lt;th>Description&lt;/th>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/thead>
 &lt;tbody>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td>&lt;code>--public-key-path&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>&lt;em>empty&lt;/em>&lt;/td>
