&lt;p>The queue path optimizes &lt;strong>producer publish latency&lt;/strong> and decoupling; LogsGo workers still perform durable ingestion on the consumer side. Choose based on whether your bottleneck is &lt;strong>app-side blocking&lt;/strong> or &lt;strong>server-side persist&lt;/strong>.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>